{
  "stem": "5371.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they said-- somebody said they-- they're shipping us to coal mines, [INAUDIBLE] which was near Buna, where they shipped a lot of Hungarian people where they died.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of them died in these coal mines.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- I let out work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, I knew somebody in camp, a Polish guy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was from Zamosc, which is a town in Poland near Czestochowa.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was there, a prominent one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had-- his number was 7638.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was there from the first ones.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was an architect, but he had to some kind-- a lot of connections there in camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he knew about me that I was put into [? the ?] barrack.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he knew somebody in the main chancellery, there in camp, and somehow he got me out from that barrack.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was-- I was put back into-- my own block.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And actually all the people from there, I don't know where they were.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If they were killed or shipped to-- to coal mines, I don't know, because it was very hard to know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "News didn't travel very fast there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In October 1944, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they put us into the empty-- where the gypsies were.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They put a-- about 700, 800 people, young people mostly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they kept us there for a couple days, and then they took us to the railroad.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we went on the railroad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We came to Stutthof, which is another [? bread ?] camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Was-- of course we heard a lot of stories there, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They brought them from Lithuania, from Latvia, Estonia, a lot of Jewish people and women by a ship and they drowned them in the Baltic Sea.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
